imdb.plot outline: The teenage, clean-shaven, younger Mario brothers, heroes of the Mushroom Kingdom, decide to take a vacation to the real world of Earth. When the two decide to stay and the pipes back to their home dimension close, they discover that by staying, they have put the whole planet in terrible danger by attracting the attention of an ancient evil. The two of them, along with many other nintendo characters, must put a stop to it before it's too late!
